\s1 Cer ka jĂ¶ n'Ă¶thĂ¶Ă¶
\p 
\v 12 Kobedi dong ka Ă«tĂŻtĂ¶ nĂŻ ecero Kiricito kĂŻ kin jĂ¶ n'Ă¶thĂ¶Ă¶, pĂŻngĂ¶ jĂ¶ mĂ¶kĂ¶ kĂŻ kinwu kobo nĂŻ cer ka jĂ¶ n'Ă¶thĂ¶Ă¶ ope?
