\v 36 In ĂŻmĂŻng! Kodhi na in ĂŻcwĂ¶ ĂŻ ngĂ¶m, ba twĂ«rĂ¶ nwongo kwĂ¶ wang n'Ă¶thĂ¶Ă¶ kono.
